<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="43" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="43">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="43">
Differing from 
<taxonomicName genus="V." lsidName="V. devergens" pageId="0" pageNumber="43" rank="species" species="devergens">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="43">V. devergens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by longer involucrellum, morphologically difficult to separate from 
<taxonomicName genus="V." lsidName="V. kuusamoensis" pageId="0" pageNumber="43" rank="species" species="kuusamoensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="43">V. kuusamoensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but the sequence divergence in ITS 5.4-6.0%.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
